<div class="learn-more-body">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="small-12 small-centered medium-8 medium-centered large-8 large-centered columns">
      <h1 id="learn_more_title">Kaizano</h1>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="small-9 medium-12 large-12 columns">
      <div class="how-it-works-text">
        <h2>Improve Your Public Speaking Skills</h2>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="small-9 medium-11 large-12 columns">
      <div class="learn-more-body">
        <h5>No matter what type of profession you're in chances are at one point or another you're going to have to give a presentation in front of an audience, Kaizano was created with the goal of allowing public speakers to connect with their audience and improve their public speaking skills. Whether you're a teacher, student, business professional, or giving your first presentation, Kaizano is the perfect tool to help you improve your public speaking skills.</h5>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="small-9 medium-8 large-8 columns">
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="small-9 medium-8 large-8 columns">
      <div class="learn-more-objects">
        <h2>Connect with your Audience</h2>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class ="row">
    <div class="small-12 medium-4 large-4 columns">
      <div class="learn-more-objects">
        <h5>Each time you give a presentation create an event on Kaizano, your audience will then be able to access the event page with the event password where they can connect with you during and after your presentation.</h5>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="small-12 medium-8 large-8 columns">
      <div class="learn-more-objects">
        <%= image_tag("kaizano_screen_shots/event_page.png", class: "screen-shot") %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="small-9 medium-8 large-8 columns">
      <div class="learn-more-objects">
        <h2>Real Honest Audience Feedback</h2>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="small-12 medium-8 large-8 columns">
      <div class="learn-more-objects">
        <%= image_tag("kaizano_screen_shots/feedback.png", class: "screen-shot") %>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="small-12 medium-4 large-4 columns">
      <div class="learn-more-objects">
        <h5>Kaizano allows for audience members to anonymously give you feedback on your presentation. Audience members can give you general feedback and rate the effectiveness of your presentation.  Use the ratings and feedback to improve your presentation skills.</h5>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="small-9 medium-8 large-12 columns">
      <div class="learn-more-objects">
        <h2>Multiple Choice Questions</h2>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="small-12 medium-4 large-4 columns">
      <div class="learn-more-objects">
        <h5>Create multiple choice questions for your audience to answer, use these questions to gage how well your audience is grasping the material you're presenting on.</h5>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="small-12 medium-8 large-8 columns">
      <div class="learn-more-objects">
        <%= image_tag("kaizano_screen_shots/multi_choice_results.png", class: "screen-shot") %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="small-9 medium-8 large-8 columns">
      <div class="learn-more-objects">
        <h2>Your Dashboard</h2>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class ="row">
    <div class="small-12 medium-8 large-8 columns">
      <div class="learn-more-objects">
        <%= image_tag("kaizano_screen_shots/profile.png", class: "screen-shot") %>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="small-12 medium-4 large-4 columns">
      <div class="learn-more-objects">
        <h5>Manage all your presentations through your private dashboard.  Review feedback from past presentations, respond to audience questions, track your improvement overtime through our analytics system, and view the results of multiple choice questions.</h5>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="get-started">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="small-9 small-centered medium-8 large-6 columns">
        <div class="full-length-button">
          <%= link_to "Get Started", new_user_registration_path, class: "button" %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>